This is a well written and presented app and one of the very few cryptic crossword apps for Android.   As for the clues, I would say they're a little too easy for me personally, I'd rate the difficulty as somewhere between the Sun's and Daily Telegraph's ones, with the occasional belter. For someone starting out on cryptics I would highly recommend this app, and for those with more experience it's still worth it for the anagram practice. And you get an enormous amount of crosswords for the price.
